Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.65,0:00:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要急
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.86,0:00:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 时间到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我通宵不睡想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解后扣比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为文化祭的节目怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.82,0:00:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这鬼东西能被允许就闹鬼了
